  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT ESTABLISHING THE STATE-MANAGED DISASTER ASSISTANCE PROGRAM TO ENABLE THE MISSISSIPPI EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT AGENCY TO ADMINISTER STATE-FUNDED EMERGENCY PREPAREDNESS, RESPONSE, AND RECOVERY; TO CREATE THE STATE-MANAGED DISASTER ASSISTANCE TRUST FUND AND PRESCRIBE ELIGIBILITY FOR FUNDS; TO PROVIDE FOR WORK PERFORMED BY CONTRACT AND THE ADVANCE OF FUNDS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
